commit_message: Warn when a dragged group column has many unique values and offer binning; add manual binning support when generating traces. AxisSideMenu: import CSV store, check unique count on drop, prompt to bin, and show a help badge next to the Group Axis label; uses GroupAxisSettings popup when binning is chosen. PlotlyHelpers: consume groupSettings from side menu data and support 'manual' binning mode by grouping rows into configured bins (creating traces per bin); preserve default per-value grouping otherwise. TopMenuBar: add a "Binning Test (Many Unique)" test dataset option and wire getBinningTestData into the loader. TestDatasets: add getBinningTestData (20 unique values) for testing binning behavior.
